    "synopsis": "With the Heresy tearing the galaxy in half, Captain Arcadese of the Ultramarines finds himself thrust into command of the Ardent Reef, a ring of gun-bastions and asteroid forts encircling Sol. As Horus's traitor fleet burns toward the Throneworld, Arcadese must hold the line against impossible odds — until the battle takes a final, unexpected turn that reveals just how the Sigillite measures the men he is about to put in charge of Terra's outer wall. A short, claustrophobic piece about duty and the weight of being tested by Malcador without knowing it.",
